@startuml sequence_detail
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Contact Detail

actor User
participant "ContactDetailPage" as UI
participant "ContactsApi" as SVC
participant "GET /api/contacts/{id}" as API
participant "AppDbContext" as CTX
database "contacts + interactions" as DB

User -> UI: tap a result card
UI -> SVC: get(id, take=3)
SVC -> API: GET /api/contacts/:id?take=3
API -> CTX: Contacts.FirstOrDefault(id)
CTX -> DB: SELECT contact
DB --> CTX: row
API -> CTX: Interactions.OrderByDesc(occurredAt).Take(3)
CTX -> DB: SELECT interactions
DB --> CTX: 3 rows
API --> SVC: ContactDetailDto
SVC --> UI: dto
UI --> User: hero + tags + timeline render

User -> UI: tap star
UI -> SVC: update(id, {starred:true})
SVC -> API: PATCH /api/contacts/:id
API -> CTX: UPDATE starred
CTX -> DB: UPDATE
DB --> CTX: ok
API --> SVC: 200
SVC --> UI: star stays filled

@enduml
